Appalled by reports of barbaric shelling near hospitals in Ukraine.

@WHOUkraine has verified 91 attacks on healthcare, causing 73 deaths &amp; 46 injuries – including health workers.

This only strengthens our resolve to give Ukraine all the support it needs. https://t.co/0Ek1A6meXp

It's #WorldDownSyndromeDay - improving the lives of people with Down Syndrome is hugely important.

@LiamFox's #DownSyndromeBill will improve the outcomes of people living with the condition &amp; has now passed its Second Reading in the @HouseofLords.

#WDSD22

I can confirm that 21 very ill Ukrainian children with cancer have landed safely in UK this evening. 

@NHSEngland will now ensure they get life-saving care in safety.

Hugely grateful to everyone involved in helping get these children and their families here.

Women should feel supported at work when they’re going through the menopause. 

@mariacaulfield spoke to @TheSun @Fabulousmag about the government’s pledge to lead the way and make sure our employees know they have our support if they need it.   

👉🏽https://t.co/En3zupEikD

Early data suggests Omicron has a reduced risk of hospitalisation.

This is good, encouraging, news that we hoped to see - but our concern remains about the impact of its extremely rapid spread.

@UKHSA will provide a briefing today but the key takeaway is clear: #GetBoostedNow! https://t.co/q3ae7KPMDU

COVID-19 UPDATE:

@UKHSA is investigating a new variant. More data is needed but we're taking precautions now.

From noon tomorrow six African countries will be added to the red list, flights will be temporarily banned, and UK travellers must quarantine.

FANTASTIC NEWS:

@WHO has approved a life-saving British malaria vaccine to be rolled out across sub-Saharan Africa - a huge step in protecting millions of children from this deadly disease.

Excellent result for the public health of the continent and for British science. @GSK https://t.co/b8ylmQh7iA

Great to meet volunteers at a COVID-19 vaccine centre last week.

@TheSun’s Jabs Army have supported our huge vaccination effort across the country – true British spirit 🇬🇧

